                <head>87. Editorial Note</head>
                <p>At its 271st meeting on December 22, the National Security Council discussed
                    controls on trade with the People’s Republic of China and the United States
                    response to the British decision to relax controls. For text of the memorandum
                    of discussion at this meeting, see <ref target="frus1955-57v03#pg_225">volume
                        III, page 225</ref>.</p>
            </div>
